Code from Dave Jarvis, Victoria, Canada Taken at http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1833252/java-stanford-nlp-part-of-speech-labels

Represents the English parts-of-speech, encoded using the de facto Penn Treebank Project standard.

See Also:
Penn Treebank Specification
